content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 2605.3 - Projects eligible for financial assistance from the fund

State Regulations

Any project sponsor seeking to construct an eligible project
may apply for financial assistance from the fund. However, no fund assistance
shall be made available to finance a project on the current DWIUP which is
scheduled to receive funding from the DWSRF. Notes
